Multi-Threaded Merge Sort

Brief:
------
This sample shows you how to a implement a merge sort using multithread concepts (pthread).

How to Compile:
---------------
	$ make

How to Run:
-----------
	$ ./TMerge
	Enter Total Number of Elements to be Sort: 5

	Enter Array Elements which to be Sort: 5 4 3 2 1
	1 2 3 4 5
	$ 
